Title: college complications (elsanna)
Author: icemagix
Summary: College life wasn't as expected. Where is the freedom of being your own individual and finally finding yourself? This never came easy especially for Elsa. Nothing but college complications and a little ice magic. this is the sequel to my wattpad story "ice cold love"on wattpad,it follows Elsa around through complications and her love for Anna. its a dramatic adventure.

Title: An Icy Love In California
Author: AGwriter
Summary: L'histoire est inspirée de NinjaElsanna. Il n'y a pas d'inceste mais de la romance voir plus.Le langage est aussi un peu vulgaire. Je n'ai trouvé aucune fan ficiton sur Elsanna en français et donc comme j'ai accroché à pas mal d'histoire du genre en AU j'ai voulu faire la mienne. J'espère que ça vous plaira, n'hésitez pas à laisser un commentaire ! If you aren't french, transalte !

Title: Anna Isn't Happy
Author: letsallshiptogether
Summary: The first chapter is merely Anna's POV of a chapter from 'Elsa is Suffering' (no, I did not ask Frac) to serve as a preview of what I'm trying to do, and this would evolve into its own story, meaning I don't intend to rewrite EiS from Anna's view. This will merely explore Anna's emotions as she tries to get close to a distant (r9k) Elsa. With incestuous lesbian lovemaking.

Title: Worlds Apart
Author: LunaArendelle
Summary: Elsa lives a complex life, dealing with depression and anxiety, while also having a disturbingly intimate relationship with her stepmother. Her days are dark as she lays alone, but things seem to start to change when Elsa meets Anna in Central Park one cold morning... Content Warning:Contains mature subject matter and themes, sexual content, and strong language.

Title: Log In
Author: queenoffrozenfractals
Summary: Elsa was just a roleplayer on Tumblr who fell in love... An Elsanna fanfic. This is my first fic on here, so please be kind! Cursing and explicit NSFW to be expected. Cover image not mine!

Title: First Encounters
Author: RachetElsaKicksAss
Summary: Modern!AU ELSANNA From the moment she first saw her, Anna knew the ice-powered blonde wasn't from her world. Alien? No. The mysterious girl was much greater than that. But with Hans and the rest of the military willing to stop at nothing to catch Elsa, will Anna be able to protect her new friend and help her adjust to the modern world? Or will she be the one needing protection?

Title: Barbarians on the Servers
Author: Rider the Writer
Summary: The so-called "meta fic" on /frz/. This essentially takes the namefriends of the Frozen General and puts them in a fantasy story. Meant to be humorous.

Title: Amor de verano
Author: Ssnow Queen 18
Summary: Elsa y Anna son dos chicas que van a pasar sus vacaciones en Arendelle con su grupo de amigos. Al verse, las dos no tardan en enamorarse. Pero ¿Qué pasara con su relación cuando terminen sus vacaciones? Sabiendo que Elsa se ira a Inglaterra al final del viaje. Elsanna

Title: Winter In Des Moines
Author: TheArtistElisey
Summary: Anna is a clumsy high school senior with a retainer that always falls out and a romantic heart. Elsa is a popular, demure high school senior who is captain of the Academic Decathlon team and "Queen" of the small town of Des Moines they live in. The two barely interact as they pass in homeroom, but a heated camping trip leads to more than either of them ever thought. Elsanna 3
